{"tid":2451020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–生病要戒口的理論推斷","createTime":"2021-03-17T22:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:26:50.000Z","uid":38861,"like":56,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3892044bf6f1c869942210afc242dc8f03993e73","tid":2451020,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T22:03:12.000Z","msg":"生病的時候需要戒口，究竟有沒有科學根據或理論基礎，還是純粹是經驗所談的學說?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKa1ENS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKa1ENS.png&h=894c138a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）當腸道內壁發炎或有所受損的時候，一系列的免疫細胞便會前來修復所損部位。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDwcMsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDwcMsZ.jpg&h=3ef26e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而位於我們腸內的有益細菌例如Arkk菌亦會釋放化學物質，例如deoxycholate，輔助免疫細胞進行修復的工作。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）在老鼠研究中，倘若在修復其間服用抗生素，那些有益細菌便會暫時性的被殲滅。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FTnSMs2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFTnSMs2.png&h=1dd67e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有證據顯示，不受抗生素影響的真菌(Debaryomyces hansenii)在這時候會釋放物質加劇及延長發炎反應，反其然減慢收復工作。<br />\n<br />\n正常的情況下，這些真菌並不會構成威脅，唯獨是腸道細菌被殲滅及腸道受損這兩點共同發生，它才會發揮它惡人的本色。<br />\n<br />\n這些真菌是否一直能長期居住在腸道內，暫時尚未清楚，至少潰瘍性結腸炎的病人腸道中的而且確是找到了這些真菌的存在，而健康人士的腸道甚少能尋覓出它的存在。<br />\n<br />\n但是，不少香腸及芝士也加上了這種真菌作加工處理，在腸道受損及服用抗生素之際，或許真的是要戒口不進食這些食物才為明智。<br />\n<br />\n而隨著對細菌、真菌及其他微生物互動的認識加深，戒口的科學基礎或許會越來越得以鞏固。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=d0d422b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=94d063c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6534/1154?ijkey=9e3b448e67a9957629ad1b99772bdc98b168368d&amp;keytype2=tf_ipsecsha\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F371%2F6534%2F1154%3Fijkey%3D9e3b448e67a9957629ad1b99772bdc98b168368d%26keytype2%3Dtf_ipsecsha&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2eNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=ed573e14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6534/1154?ijkey=9e3b448e67a9957629ad1b99772bdc98b168368d&amp;keytype2=tf_ipsecsha</a>"},{"pid":"02f8fa7652cc89eccb8c99ec8dfa95a9bc73856e","tid":2451020,"uid":95519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T22:10:54.000Z","msg":"屌最鐘意食芝士腸<br />\nJohnsonville嘅好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fe5994c1bf577f9f37f6ca0aad2cba2d22bccd","tid":2451020,"uid":38861,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"02f8fa7652cc89eccb8c99ec8dfa95a9bc73856e","tid":2451020,"uid":95519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T22:10:54.000Z","msg":"屌最鐘意食芝士腸<br />\nJohnsonville嘅好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":